reviewText:
What a wonderful show! The music was  great. A number of popular performers and groups joined in on several songs. It was a lot of fun and Bruno y Marrone were exceptional!

The seller, MusicGlobo, was very helpful when I was confused about the DVD. I mistakenly thought I had ordered a CD. (Dumb!)Great service and a lot of patience from them. I highly recommend this supplier.
This is absolutely awesome!!!  I have watched it at least 8 times if not more.  Fantastic .
